  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of ghee or oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onions and sauté until they start to brown.",
    "Add the mung beans and pilaf rice, and stir to coat with the oil.",
    "Add the turmeric and coriander, and stir for 1-2 minutes.",
    "Add 2 cups of water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover, and simmer for 15-20 minutes.",
